          <declname>task</declname>
        </param>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Cooperative task for resolving a hostname via DNS. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Register this as a SYN_TaskFunc with user_data pointing to a <ref refid="structSYN__DnsResolver" kindref="compound">SYN_DnsResolver</ref> instance. The task runs non-blocking UDP queries, yielding via PT_YIELD until resolution completes or times out.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>pt</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Protothread pointer. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>task</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Task structure whose user_data points to a <ref refid="structSYN__DnsResolver" kindref="compound">SYN_DnsResolver</ref>. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="return"><para>PT_WAITING while running, PT_EXITED when done, or PT_ENDED on early exit. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
